txt.en: 'I was just remembering how Bucco used to come up the walk after a day in the fields.'
'I was just doing a little baking, and of course I made too much, so I brought you some.'
'Oh, how sweet of you! You shouldn't have.'
'Well, I must be running along now. Enjoy the cakes!'
'Thank you, I'm sure Brundo will be delighted to find them when he gets home.'
'Very well, thank you. And how are you?'
